parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the key to be removed from the ignition while the vehicle is running, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded. Additionally, the ignition switch may jam or become difficult to turn, making it hard to start or shut off the vehicle.
symptoms: The key can be removed from the ignition while the vehicle is running
the key is difficult to turn to start or shut off the vehicle
the ignition switch jams or becomes stuck
the key falls out of the ignition while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A dashboard fire can cause significant damage to the vehicle and potentially lead to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The dashboard is on fire.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates
the vehicle loses power
the transmission makes a grinding noise
the vehicle cannot shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch and slave cylinder can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a delayed return to its normal position.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS system can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents.
symptoms: The ABS system light is on
the vehicle vibrates or shakes when braking
the brakes malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the vehicle to stall or not start, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The key gets stuck in the ignition
the key falls out of the ignition
the ignition switch is difficult to turn.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The steering column lock-up can cause loss of steering control, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Steering wheel locks up
key gets stuck in ignition
unable to turn key
steering column physically locks up.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the engine to shut off while driving, leading to loss of control and accidents.
symptoms: Key can be removed from ignition while engine is running
engine shuts off while driving
ignition switch locks up
key gets stuck in ignition.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electronic steering control can cause loss of power steering, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Hesitation to drive forward after turning
power steering failure
electronic steering control malfunction.
